WEBVTT

01:27.380 --> 01:31.950
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.160 --> 01:34.950
[Episode 21]

01:35.560 --> 01:37.920
No one can separate us.

01:36.600 --> 01:40.840
[Outpatient Clinic]

01:40.400 --> 01:42.870
No one can separate us.

02:16.430 --> 02:17.840
You bad girl!

02:17.840 --> 02:19.670
You're even trying to scare me?

02:19.710 --> 02:20.960
You're even trying to scare me?

02:20.960 --> 02:21.960
Where are you running?

02:21.960 --> 02:23.220
Where are you running?

02:24.240 --> 02:25.120
Stop running!

02:26.560 --> 02:27.560
Have you finished your homework?

02:27.560 --> 02:28.490
Yes, I have.

02:28.520 --> 02:29.280
Are you hungry?

02:29.280 --> 02:29.840
Yes, I am.

02:30.310 --> 02:31.630
I want to have some Sugar-Oil Fritters.

02:31.630 --> 02:33.000
Wait here. I'll go buy some for you.

02:33.000 --> 02:33.610
Love you.

02:46.630 --> 02:47.470
Zishan.

02:49.190 --> 02:49.750
Zishan.

03:00.330 --> 03:01.150
Zishan.

03:03.150 --> 03:03.960
Doctor...

03:05.960 --> 03:06.960
Dr. Luo.

03:09.240 --> 03:10.440
You remember who I am.

03:12.360 --> 03:14.020
Have you recalled something?

03:28.750 --> 03:30.190
Predestination

03:32.560 --> 03:35.400
is the best gift

03:36.840 --> 03:38.370
from Heaven to us.

03:39.000 --> 03:42.820
Our meeting is predestined.

03:44.470 --> 03:45.440
The two of us

03:47.310 --> 03:49.870
are the best gifts
from Heaven to each other.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.190
Liang.

04:18.310 --> 04:18.829
It's me.

04:21.430 --> 04:21.959
I'm here.

04:23.950 --> 04:25.210
I've always been here.

04:26.900 --> 04:28.370
I've never left you.

04:35.030 --> 04:37.650
[Qingzhu Hotel]

04:36.360 --> 04:37.190
Who is it?

04:37.190 --> 04:38.390
I'm the housekeeper.

04:38.920 --> 04:39.720
Coming.

04:43.480 --> 04:44.360
Ms. Hua.

04:44.430 --> 04:45.510
The luggage you lost

04:45.510 --> 04:47.040
has been brought back by the shuttle bus.

04:47.040 --> 04:47.800
Thank you.

04:49.430 --> 04:51.159
Alright then. I'm leaving now.

04:57.630 --> 04:58.430
Mom.

05:02.950 --> 05:05.190
Check if everything is here.

05:14.800 --> 05:15.930
Everything's here.

05:18.680 --> 05:19.630
Luo and I...

05:22.830 --> 05:25.290
Xiao Su and I have just got married.

05:25.360 --> 05:27.560
He probably hasn't had time to tell you.

05:27.830 --> 05:29.160
He has told me about it,

05:29.600 --> 05:30.660
saying that you are

05:30.750 --> 05:32.040
a university teacher

05:32.040 --> 05:34.100
and are well-educated and sensible.

05:36.750 --> 05:37.720
Where is Su?

05:38.270 --> 05:39.350
Is he also here?

05:40.659 --> 05:41.450
Yes.

05:42.159 --> 05:43.310
He knew that you

05:43.360 --> 05:45.620
had taken Qiao Zishan from the hospital.

05:45.950 --> 05:47.080
He was very anxious,

05:47.560 --> 05:49.430
so he rushed over here immediately.

05:49.430 --> 05:49.920
Then...

05:50.190 --> 05:50.990
Has he

05:51.070 --> 05:52.390
found Zishan yet?

05:53.560 --> 05:54.490
Yes, he has.

05:55.830 --> 05:57.040
Where are they now?

05:57.270 --> 05:59.000
Are they alone together?

05:59.330 --> 06:00.700
Take me to see him now.

06:02.750 --> 06:04.280
What are you worried about?

06:08.720 --> 06:11.360
Why did you take Qiao Zishan away

06:12.160 --> 06:13.560
without telling Xiao Su?

06:16.510 --> 06:18.370
Are you worried about Qiao Zishan

06:19.040 --> 06:20.310
or Xiao Su?

06:26.190 --> 06:27.000
Liang.

06:29.680 --> 06:30.430
Mom.

06:35.920 --> 06:37.050
I'm looking for Mom.

06:38.270 --> 06:39.070
Where is Mom?

06:43.360 --> 06:44.360
Your mom is dead.

06:46.430 --> 06:47.560
Don't you remember?

06:54.360 --> 06:55.750
You killed your mom.

06:56.560 --> 06:57.960
Have you forgotten that?

06:58.270 --> 06:59.430
I'm looking for Mom.

07:00.830 --> 07:02.360
Your mom was burnt to death.

07:06.830 --> 07:08.230
Your mom died miserably.

07:09.510 --> 07:10.910
And it was all your fault.

07:14.510 --> 07:15.560
It was a big fire.

07:17.870 --> 07:19.470
It was really such a big fire.

07:21.050 --> 07:21.790
Why?

07:23.240 --> 07:24.570
Why didn't you save her?

07:26.240 --> 07:27.440
It was such a big fire.

07:31.490 --> 07:33.110
Why did you kill your mom?

07:35.360 --> 07:35.950
Zishan.

07:37.409 --> 07:38.610
Have you recalled it?

07:39.560 --> 07:41.690
You took such good care of Qiao Zishan.

07:42.159 --> 07:44.560
How would you misremember her drug dosage?

07:45.240 --> 07:46.750
I was muddle-headed.

07:46.750 --> 07:48.190
It was all my fault. I...

07:48.560 --> 07:50.360
But your plan was very thorough.

07:50.870 --> 07:53.330
You brought Qiao Zishan
all the way out here,

07:53.390 --> 07:56.450
and neither the hospital
nor Xiao Su found out about it.

08:00.100 --> 08:01.930
Take me to see Zishan.

08:03.190 --> 08:06.510
You're very worried about
the two of them being together, right?

08:06.510 --> 08:08.480
No, no.

08:08.480 --> 08:10.610
You were the one who burnt her to death.

08:13.870 --> 08:15.450
You just watched her burnt to death

08:15.450 --> 08:16.250
by the fire

08:17.450 --> 08:18.760
and did nothing.

08:19.440 --> 08:20.970
Your mom was in so much pain.

08:21.600 --> 08:22.160
No.

08:23.560 --> 08:25.290
She couldn't escape from there

08:25.680 --> 08:26.950
and was just burnt to death like that.

08:26.950 --> 08:27.510
No.

08:28.040 --> 08:28.790
Mom!

08:29.040 --> 08:29.950
Mom!

08:30.920 --> 08:33.039
Xiao Su is her psychiatrist.

08:34.120 --> 08:35.240
He was the one who told you what medicine

08:35.240 --> 08:36.120
and what dosage

08:36.630 --> 08:38.789
should be taken every day, right?

08:42.080 --> 08:42.870
You noticed that Qiao Zishan still

08:42.870 --> 08:45.800
didn't get any better
after taking so much medicine,

08:46.840 --> 08:48.570
so you took her to the hospital.

08:49.860 --> 08:51.920
But the police discovered a problem.

08:52.330 --> 08:54.260
Do you know how much pain she was in?

08:55.670 --> 08:57.270
You would be in pain too, huh?

08:57.360 --> 08:59.590
But your mother's pain was 10 times
or even 100 times stronger than yours.

08:59.590 --> 09:00.750
When she was found,

09:00.960 --> 09:02.620
she didn't have any skin left.

09:03.030 --> 09:04.720
But Xiao Su is your son.

09:06.340 --> 09:09.200
And you couldn't tell the police
these suspicions.

09:09.550 --> 09:12.410
-Zishan.
-But you also want to protect Qiao Zishan.

09:12.510 --> 09:14.770
So you could only take her away secretly.

09:15.510 --> 09:16.320
Is that right?

09:16.360 --> 09:17.840
How could you kill your mom?

09:17.840 --> 09:19.430
-I didn't!
-Why did you kill your mom?

09:19.430 --> 09:20.980
Why did you kill her?

09:21.270 --> 09:23.320
It would be great if Mom has disappeared.

09:23.320 --> 09:25.320
No! No!

09:26.080 --> 09:27.840
Mom!

09:27.880 --> 09:29.910
Mom, I'm sorry!

09:30.670 --> 09:32.600
Xiao Su isn't like this.

09:32.670 --> 09:34.040
No!

09:35.080 --> 09:37.200
Mom!

09:37.840 --> 09:40.440
Mom!

09:42.030 --> 09:42.870
Xiao Su

09:44.320 --> 09:45.980
wasn't like this originally.

09:54.320 --> 09:56.200
It was all because of his father.

09:57.270 --> 09:58.360
After his sister

09:58.720 --> 10:00.630
was taken away for a few years,

10:01.480 --> 10:03.120
she finally came back.

10:04.320 --> 10:05.780
I originally thought that

10:06.000 --> 10:06.870
everything

10:07.030 --> 10:08.810
was going to get better.

10:18.270 --> 10:18.840
Su.

10:25.670 --> 10:26.890
-Sister?
-Yuan?

10:28.320 --> 10:28.840
Mom.

10:34.840 --> 10:35.750
I brought you a gift.

10:35.750 --> 10:36.750
See if you like it.

10:40.320 --> 10:43.200
I specifically had it blessed
by Wong Tai Sin on Harbor Island.

10:43.200 --> 10:44.900
Mom, this is for you.

10:45.120 --> 10:46.520
There's a gift for me too?

10:48.910 --> 10:50.000
Study hard

10:50.000 --> 10:51.510
to get a good score.

10:52.910 --> 10:55.080
Why didn't you die outside?

10:57.550 --> 10:58.910
You're such a disgrace.

10:59.930 --> 11:02.660
Dressing like this,
who are you trying to seduce?

11:05.630 --> 11:06.810
It cost over 300 HK dollars.

11:06.810 --> 11:09.610
[Xinhua Dictionary]

11:07.860 --> 11:10.060
Who did you sleep with to get this money?

11:14.960 --> 11:15.840
You little scoundrel!

11:15.840 --> 11:16.840
What are you doing?

11:16.840 --> 11:17.320
What happened?

11:17.320 --> 11:17.960
What happened?

11:17.960 --> 11:19.200
What's on your underpants?

11:19.200 --> 11:20.240
I'll beat you to death!

11:20.240 --> 11:21.200
Don't hit him.

11:21.200 --> 11:22.870
I didn't do anything. I just had a dream.

11:22.870 --> 11:25.000
If you keep hitting him like this,
I'll take him away!

11:25.000 --> 11:26.960
And you'll never be able to find us again!

11:26.960 --> 11:28.690
Think you're all grown up, huh?

11:28.720 --> 11:30.120
All of you can just leave!

11:30.390 --> 11:31.590
You think I don't know

11:31.630 --> 11:32.550
how you earned

11:32.750 --> 11:34.320
that dirty money of yours, huh?

11:34.320 --> 11:36.530
Get lost! Get lost, all of you!

11:36.630 --> 11:37.320
Look at you.

11:37.550 --> 11:38.360
As soon as you came back,

11:38.360 --> 11:40.090
your brother became like this.

11:40.390 --> 11:41.720
How shameless!

11:42.360 --> 11:42.890
No.

11:43.750 --> 11:45.220
I just had a dream.

11:46.040 --> 11:47.970
I really don't know what happened.

11:53.030 --> 11:53.870
Yuan!

11:54.510 --> 11:55.050
Sister!

11:55.270 --> 11:55.990
Sister!

11:56.480 --> 11:57.080
Sister!

11:57.510 --> 11:58.870
Su! Su!

11:59.870 --> 12:00.650
I'll never

12:00.870 --> 12:02.390
come back to this home again!

12:02.390 --> 12:03.030
Sister!

12:03.510 --> 12:04.510
Wait for me!

12:05.670 --> 12:06.270
Sister!

12:07.150 --> 12:08.810
Take me with you to leave here!

12:08.840 --> 12:09.720
His father...

12:11.270 --> 12:14.080
was a dirty-minded beast himself.

12:16.030 --> 12:16.670
So,

12:18.130 --> 12:20.390
he thought everyone else was dirty, too.

12:22.140 --> 12:23.140
Xiao Su

12:25.210 --> 12:26.260
and his sister

12:30.200 --> 12:32.080
were both ruined by him.

12:43.130 --> 12:44.480
Step back, everyone!

12:44.480 --> 12:46.240
Guys, please cooperate!

12:50.120 --> 12:51.520
Guys, please cooperate!

12:51.960 --> 12:53.030
Don't block the way, you all.

12:53.030 --> 12:55.230
Step aside! Let me through! Step aside!

13:05.270 --> 13:06.430
We found Qiao Zishan.

13:06.430 --> 13:08.030
She's at the police station.

13:09.000 --> 13:09.530
Let's go.

13:10.630 --> 13:11.300
Hurry up!

13:11.630 --> 13:12.440
Be careful!

13:15.880 --> 13:18.030
[Xincheng Police Station, Kangjia Road Branch,
Tanhua Public Security Bureau]

13:28.330 --> 13:30.600
[Case Filing Chamber,
Sunday, July 21, 2019]

13:30.650 --> 13:33.670
[Police]

13:33.320 --> 13:35.190
Let go of her! Let go!

13:35.480 --> 13:36.880
Zishan! Zishan! Come on!

13:38.910 --> 13:39.550
No!

13:40.120 --> 13:42.290
It's okay. I'm here.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.080
Zishan.

13:44.080 --> 13:45.080
We are the police.

13:46.270 --> 13:47.000
Come with us.

13:47.840 --> 13:49.790
The police will protect you
and keep you safe.

13:49.790 --> 13:50.410
Okay?

13:51.080 --> 13:52.340
Don't get close to her.

13:52.510 --> 13:54.200
She's emotionally unstable now.

13:54.200 --> 13:55.720
If I was one minute late at that time,

13:55.720 --> 13:58.250
she would've jumped down
from that buidling.

14:00.120 --> 14:00.670
Zishan.

14:02.200 --> 14:02.840
Zishan.

14:03.790 --> 14:05.390
We've met before. Remember?

14:06.840 --> 14:07.600
Don't worry.

14:08.480 --> 14:09.270
If someone tries to hurt you,

14:09.270 --> 14:10.130
you can tell me,

14:10.480 --> 14:12.280
and I'll definitely arrest him.

14:13.150 --> 14:14.350
Come with the police.

14:17.790 --> 14:19.440
The police will protect you
and keep you safe.

14:19.440 --> 14:19.870
Okay?

14:26.200 --> 14:28.360
I killed my mom!

14:30.510 --> 14:32.240
Mom... I killed

14:32.240 --> 14:32.860
my mom!

14:33.670 --> 14:35.400
Now that she has become like this,

14:35.400 --> 14:37.660
you guys are largely responsible for it.

14:37.920 --> 14:39.550
My mom said she was fine at first.

14:39.550 --> 14:40.630
Without considering

14:40.630 --> 14:41.670
her condition,

14:41.670 --> 14:43.150
you guys forcibly hypnotized her.

14:43.150 --> 14:45.550
We've evaluated the risks
of hypnotizing her.

14:45.550 --> 14:47.600
The police's case-handling procedures
are reasonable and lawful.

14:47.600 --> 14:49.260
We don't need to report to you.

14:50.390 --> 14:51.190
Let me ask you.

14:51.670 --> 14:53.870
Why did your mom take her away secretly?

14:55.960 --> 14:57.290
Because my mom knew that

14:57.910 --> 14:59.970
if you found out she was not my sister,

15:00.210 --> 15:01.320
you would take away

15:01.320 --> 15:03.120
her only spiritual sustenance.

15:06.120 --> 15:07.780
If you cared about her so much,

15:08.110 --> 15:10.910
why did your mom take her away
without telling you?

15:11.240 --> 15:11.940
Mom.

15:12.000 --> 15:13.600
Because my mom knew very well

15:13.910 --> 15:15.910
I wouldn't let her take Zishan away.

15:16.960 --> 15:17.600
When she disappeared,

15:17.600 --> 15:19.530
you should have called the police.

15:19.870 --> 15:21.330
If I had called the police,

15:21.360 --> 15:23.360
wouldn't my mom become an abductor?

15:23.960 --> 15:25.750
But now that I've found Zishan,

15:26.000 --> 15:28.000
my mom's problem is not that serious.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.420
Right, Officer Li?

15:32.960 --> 15:34.870
I don't believe in a single word you say,

15:34.870 --> 15:35.670
Dr. Luo.

15:38.350 --> 15:40.080
-Don't worry. I'm here.
-Mom.

15:40.080 --> 15:40.810
Where's Mom?

15:42.960 --> 15:43.600
Mom.

15:47.790 --> 15:48.390
Mom.

15:48.790 --> 15:50.550
No!

15:51.910 --> 15:53.030
Mom!

15:53.510 --> 15:55.540
Mom!

15:55.630 --> 15:57.480
Mom!

15:58.550 --> 15:59.870
Mom!

16:01.790 --> 16:02.440
Hello?

16:03.120 --> 16:04.450
The police has found me.

16:04.480 --> 16:06.070
I think they've tracked down your car.

16:06.070 --> 16:07.330
They'll find you soon.

16:08.150 --> 16:08.720
Mom!

16:09.440 --> 16:10.150
Mom!

16:11.030 --> 16:12.000
Mom!

16:13.120 --> 16:13.680
Mom!

16:13.910 --> 16:15.570
Mom!

16:16.600 --> 16:17.390
Mom!

16:18.000 --> 16:19.030
Mom!

16:19.790 --> 16:21.320
Mom!

16:22.720 --> 16:24.380
No one will forgive you,

16:24.400 --> 16:25.320
except me.

16:27.510 --> 16:30.770
I'm the one who understands you the best
in the whole world.

16:31.360 --> 16:32.280
I know you well.

16:32.960 --> 16:33.960
I'll forgive you.

16:36.720 --> 16:38.120
I won't let anyone know

16:38.470 --> 16:40.470
that you've killed someone before.

16:41.560 --> 16:42.960
For the rest of your life,

16:43.420 --> 16:44.820
you must always remember

16:45.870 --> 16:47.870
you were the one who killed your mom.

16:48.910 --> 16:50.940
You were the one who killed your mom.

16:57.020 --> 16:59.320
I was the one who killed my mom.

17:05.030 --> 17:05.920
I'm sorry.

17:07.690 --> 17:08.440
I'm sorry.

17:09.000 --> 17:10.160
I'm sorry.

17:10.640 --> 17:11.310
I'm sorry.

17:13.349 --> 17:15.170
Mom! Mom!

17:17.480 --> 17:18.240
Mom!

17:19.589 --> 17:20.640
I killed her.

17:21.200 --> 17:22.810
I killed her!

17:23.109 --> 17:24.109
Mom!

17:24.050 --> 17:26.200
[Xincheng Police Station, Kangjia Road Branch,
Tanhua Public Security Bureau]

17:41.570 --> 17:43.080
[Please go upstairs from this way]

17:43.080 --> 17:44.530
[No smoking]

17:45.880 --> 17:47.690
Officers,
there's no need to trouble you two.

17:47.690 --> 17:49.690
I can explain it to my mother myself.

17:50.350 --> 17:51.510
This is no trouble at all.

17:51.510 --> 17:53.170
We need to handle it to the end.

18:10.310 --> 18:11.110
Honey.

18:15.830 --> 18:17.270
Why are you two together?

18:19.440 --> 18:20.500
As soon as you left,

18:20.680 --> 18:23.310
I got a call from Officer Li,
and he was looking for you.

18:23.310 --> 18:25.970
He said they got a notice
from the Wuzhou police.

18:26.350 --> 18:28.520
Mom took Qiao Zishan away.

18:28.680 --> 18:31.720
They both went to Tanhua,
and he asked whether you knew it.

18:31.720 --> 18:32.960
I couldn't find you.

18:33.350 --> 18:35.950
I got so worried
that I just came here directly.

18:38.510 --> 18:40.170
I'm sorry to have worried you.

18:41.440 --> 18:43.000
Mom, are you okay?

18:47.830 --> 18:49.480
Everything's been clearly explained now,

18:49.480 --> 18:50.270
officers.

18:52.640 --> 18:54.510
Ma'am, why did you take Qiao Zishan away?

18:54.510 --> 18:55.310
Officer Li,

18:55.720 --> 18:57.380
whatever misunderstandings

18:57.510 --> 18:59.240
you might have about us before,

18:59.720 --> 19:02.050
we have cooperated in every way we should.

19:02.240 --> 19:03.440
If you have any proof,

19:03.590 --> 19:05.000
just arrest him.

19:05.270 --> 19:06.240
If you don't,

19:06.750 --> 19:08.010
please leave us alone.

19:08.550 --> 19:09.770
Luo Liang rushed over

19:10.070 --> 19:11.350
and found Qiao Zishan.

19:11.680 --> 19:14.090
My mother-in-law made a foolish mistake
by taking her away,

19:14.090 --> 19:15.920
but nothing serious happened in the end.

19:15.920 --> 19:16.640
Right?

19:18.160 --> 19:19.090
I implore you

19:19.960 --> 19:21.420
to end the whole thing now.

19:22.270 --> 19:23.030
Ms. Yan...

19:23.440 --> 19:25.170
If you do think of me as a friend,

19:26.270 --> 19:27.800
then don't hurt us anymore.

19:29.000 --> 19:31.260
Stop hurting my husband, in particular.

19:35.830 --> 19:37.360
Just like me, it was not easy

19:38.200 --> 19:40.260
for Luo Liang to get where he is today.

19:41.070 --> 19:42.530
Put an end to this fuss now,

19:42.680 --> 19:43.210
will you?

19:49.070 --> 19:49.440
Mom.

19:49.590 --> 19:50.190
Ms. Yan...

19:50.310 --> 19:52.160
My wife has made it very clear.

19:52.750 --> 19:54.480
Target me if anything comes up.

19:55.160 --> 19:56.690
Just leave my family alone.

20:01.070 --> 20:02.410
My number is on this card.

20:02.410 --> 20:03.140
[Name: Li Zhiheng]

20:03.550 --> 20:05.160
I'll contact you anytime

20:05.160 --> 20:06.890
if your cooperation is needed.

20:09.070 --> 20:10.350
Mom, let's go.

20:11.110 --> 20:11.720
Let me carry it.

20:11.720 --> 20:13.110
Let's go, Mom.

20:26.550 --> 20:27.810
What is all this about?

20:31.310 --> 20:32.110
Has Ms. Yan...

20:33.440 --> 20:34.900
really been brainwashed?

20:36.160 --> 20:39.190
[Nanhuguan Long-distance
Passenger Transport Station]

20:38.960 --> 20:40.030
About Zishan...

20:42.240 --> 20:43.880
She has been taken away by the police.

20:43.880 --> 20:44.790
-Thank you.
-They'll take care of her.

20:44.790 --> 20:46.920
-Don't worry.
-That's the bus, right?

20:46.920 --> 20:49.650
You didn't let anything slip to Yan Ling,
did you?

20:50.920 --> 20:52.550
Mom, here's your ticket.

20:56.960 --> 20:59.330
Actually, Luo Liang and I
have talked about it.

20:59.330 --> 21:00.480
If you want to,

21:00.510 --> 21:02.140
just come home with us.

21:02.020 --> 21:04.690
[Jinhu Transport]

21:03.640 --> 21:04.440
Yes, Mom.

21:05.480 --> 21:07.740
Yan Ling and I will respect your opinion.

21:10.180 --> 21:11.790
I'd better go back.

21:12.920 --> 21:13.840
That will

21:14.430 --> 21:15.490
put my mind at ease.

21:16.350 --> 21:18.400
I agree. Let Mom go back.

21:19.070 --> 21:21.070
Only Diannan feels like home to her.

21:27.350 --> 21:29.070
Make sure you treat Ling well.

21:31.270 --> 21:31.970
Of course.

21:32.350 --> 21:33.680
She's my wife after all.

21:38.460 --> 21:40.090
Take care.

21:42.510 --> 21:44.110
Don't compromise yourself.

21:49.790 --> 21:51.090
Mom, get on the bus now.

21:51.510 --> 21:52.640
It's about to leave.

21:56.070 --> 21:57.800
I'll visit you when I have time.

22:51.510 --> 22:52.440
Su!

22:54.510 --> 22:55.350
Yuan!

23:02.580 --> 23:03.280
Su...

23:37.240 --> 23:38.170
Thank you so much

23:38.830 --> 23:41.490
for defending me
in front of the police just now.

23:41.510 --> 23:42.840
As you just said,

23:43.550 --> 23:44.880
I am your wife after all.

23:46.750 --> 23:48.210
Ever since my sister left,

23:48.790 --> 23:50.720
no one has protected me like you do.

23:53.110 --> 23:53.970
Let the bygones

23:54.880 --> 23:56.240
be bygones.

24:07.440 --> 24:08.240
Let's go home.

25:28.210 --> 25:32.030
[List of devices]

25:44.940 --> 25:49.800
[July 20, 2019, Saturday]

25:52.260 --> 25:56.690
[July 20, 2019, Saturday]

26:01.330 --> 26:04.640
[July 20, 2019, Saturday]

26:04.660 --> 26:09.530
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

26:13.460 --> 26:19.340
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

26:15.000 --> 26:16.550
Sir, it's fixed, right?

26:16.590 --> 26:18.190
-Yes, all fixed.
-Let me see.

26:19.550 --> 26:20.550
The power is back.

26:20.590 --> 26:21.160
Thank you.

26:21.160 --> 26:21.640
No problem.

26:21.640 --> 26:22.160
Thanks.

26:22.270 --> 26:25.000
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

26:28.100 --> 26:35.690
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

26:29.510 --> 26:30.030
Hello,

26:30.570 --> 26:31.400
Officer Li.

26:33.920 --> 26:35.680
I don't know if he knows.

26:35.790 --> 26:36.310
Okay.

26:37.000 --> 26:37.930
I'll try.

26:38.680 --> 26:39.400
No problem.

26:39.840 --> 26:43.040
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

26:55.990 --> 27:00.090
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

27:04.530 --> 27:11.810
[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

27:25.880 --> 27:26.410
Hey,

27:26.440 --> 27:27.700
property management?

27:27.830 --> 27:28.420
Hello.

27:29.510 --> 27:31.570
I'm the owner of Unit 808, Building B.

27:31.750 --> 27:32.720
I'd like to ask

27:33.240 --> 27:35.570
why the power suddenly went out
at my place

27:35.750 --> 27:37.010
the night before last.

27:37.590 --> 27:39.450
Is there any maintenance record?

27:41.200 --> 27:42.310
The fuse was blown?

27:44.400 --> 27:46.460
A short circuit in the incoming wire?

27:49.830 --> 27:50.440
Got it.

27:51.680 --> 27:52.350
Thank you.

28:07.640 --> 28:08.640
Look at each other,

28:08.640 --> 28:10.070
with deep affection.

28:10.070 --> 28:12.240
One, two, three. Terrific!

28:12.310 --> 28:12.960
One more photo.

28:12.960 --> 28:14.750
One, two, three. Good!

28:14.750 --> 28:16.030
Puff out your chests a bit more. Yes.

28:16.030 --> 28:17.350
Puff out your chests, please.

28:17.350 --> 28:18.670
One, two, three.

28:18.790 --> 28:20.720
Okay. Look each other in the eye again.

28:20.720 --> 28:22.640
One, two, three. Here it goes!

28:22.720 --> 28:23.510
You're doing great.

28:23.510 --> 28:24.000
That's right.

28:24.000 --> 28:24.790
I like the vibes.

28:24.790 --> 28:25.510
Very good.

28:25.510 --> 28:27.210
This is so nice. Alright!

28:27.400 --> 28:28.640
Good. Look at me now.

28:28.920 --> 28:31.170
Okay. One, two, three.

28:45.720 --> 28:46.800
This way, please.

28:50.680 --> 28:51.830
The bride takes this room.

28:51.830 --> 28:52.160
Okay.

28:53.680 --> 28:55.000
And the groom takes this one.

28:55.000 --> 28:55.800
Okay, thanks.

28:57.590 --> 28:58.200
Honey.

29:05.480 --> 29:06.080
What's up?

29:09.720 --> 29:10.510
The last time

29:11.400 --> 29:13.660
we tried to get our wedding photos taken,

29:13.680 --> 29:15.280
your mother had an accident.

29:15.310 --> 29:17.710
I never brought up
the photo shooting again

29:18.160 --> 29:19.620
for fear of upsetting you.

29:21.920 --> 29:24.850
But this time,
you took the initiative to propose it.

29:25.440 --> 29:26.440
I'm very touched.

29:33.790 --> 29:36.650
We are going to spend
the rest of our lives together.

29:36.960 --> 29:38.960
Had better tie up all the loose ends.

29:48.790 --> 29:49.920
I'll go get changed.

29:49.960 --> 29:50.640
Okay.

29:55.640 --> 29:56.930
[Outpatient Clinic]

29:58.670 --> 30:00.780
[Outpatient Clinic]

30:00.850 --> 30:04.670
[Emergency, Impatient Department]

30:04.710 --> 30:09.770
[Exit]

30:09.900 --> 30:14.340
[Emergency, Impatient Department]

30:14.420 --> 30:17.110
[July 24, 2019, Wednesday]

30:22.280 --> 30:24.580
[July 24, 2019, Wednesday]

30:32.510 --> 30:34.830
[July 24, 2019, Wednesday]

30:48.590 --> 30:49.120
Morning.

30:50.410 --> 30:53.750
[July 25, 2019 Thursday]

30:57.410 --> 31:00.820
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

31:05.930 --> 31:06.590
Chen,

31:07.400 --> 31:09.310
get a glycerin enema to Bed 53.

31:09.360 --> 31:11.820
The patient said
he is a little constipated.

31:41.190 --> 31:43.160
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

32:29.400 --> 32:30.410
If you miss Jiale,

32:30.960 --> 32:32.050
just call him.

32:32.880 --> 32:33.720
As his mother,

32:34.240 --> 32:36.040
you should take the initiative.

32:38.790 --> 32:39.810
I'd rather not.

32:41.160 --> 32:43.680
I'm afraid Jiale hasn't forgiven me yet.

32:48.510 --> 32:50.480
It's said that a mother and child
share a special bond.

32:50.480 --> 32:51.810
Jiale is a sensible kid.

32:52.400 --> 32:55.330
No matter how angry he was,
he should be over it by now.

33:01.240 --> 33:03.440
I'll make the call for you, if you don't.

33:05.200 --> 33:07.140
[Jiale]

33:18.270 --> 33:18.880
Hello?

33:21.270 --> 33:22.110
Jiale,

33:22.640 --> 33:23.550
this is Mom.

33:24.440 --> 33:25.510
I miss you.

33:33.310 --> 33:35.410
A day apart feels like three years.

33:36.550 --> 33:37.400
Jiale,

33:38.030 --> 33:39.310
your mom misses you so much

33:39.310 --> 33:41.170
that she's aging into an old lady.

33:45.110 --> 33:48.000
Jiale, I admit I was wrong.

33:48.440 --> 33:49.510
Can you forgive me?

33:55.590 --> 33:56.850
How about this, Jiale?

33:57.310 --> 33:59.320
We'll take you hiking in a few days.

33:59.510 --> 34:01.590
Your mom and I will pick you up, okay?

34:02.730 --> 34:04.040
The weather's too hot lately.

34:04.040 --> 34:05.090
I don't want to go.

34:05.830 --> 34:07.920
No problem. It's up to you.

34:16.389 --> 34:18.989
I'll call you again in a few days,
little buddy.

34:19.590 --> 34:20.190
Bye.

34:20.760 --> 34:21.550
Bye, big bro.

34:32.230 --> 34:34.000
He's still mad at me.

34:35.320 --> 34:36.110
It's okay.

34:37.440 --> 34:38.770
Give him some more time.

35:20.710 --> 35:21.910
What are you cooking?

35:22.510 --> 35:23.510
Small wontons.

35:24.710 --> 35:25.550
Try some.

35:26.230 --> 35:26.960
Sure.

35:26.960 --> 35:28.000
Careful, it's hot.

35:28.000 --> 35:28.800
Okay.

35:29.110 --> 35:30.110
Here's cilantro.

35:42.280 --> 35:42.920
So tasty.

35:56.230 --> 35:57.030
Are you happy?

35:58.800 --> 35:59.480
What?

36:01.670 --> 36:02.600
That pen holder.

36:03.320 --> 36:05.440
I found it in Mom's bag that day.

36:06.590 --> 36:08.550
She said you got it from your sister
as a gift,

36:08.550 --> 36:10.030
and that you liked it so much

36:10.030 --> 36:11.440
that you'd take it everywhere with you.

36:11.440 --> 36:13.710
It was not until you started working
that you sent it back home.

36:13.710 --> 36:16.110
I know you were very close
with your sister,

36:16.850 --> 36:18.710
so I asked Mom for this pen holder.

36:21.630 --> 36:23.560
Why didn't you tell me beforehand?

36:25.030 --> 36:26.890
Because I wanted to surprise you.

36:34.110 --> 36:35.440
I noticed

36:35.710 --> 36:36.640
the broken parts

36:37.150 --> 36:38.010
here and there.

36:38.230 --> 36:40.550
I meant to have the item fixed
before bringing it back to you.

36:40.550 --> 36:41.950
However, I asked around—

36:42.230 --> 36:45.150
watch repairers, appliance repairers,
car mechanics—

36:45.150 --> 36:46.460
but no one could fix it.

36:46.840 --> 36:48.640
So I had to bring it back as it was.

36:51.480 --> 36:52.280
Thank you.

37:02.840 --> 37:04.030
Are you not happy?

37:07.280 --> 37:08.280
Why would I not be?

37:44.490 --> 37:50.190
[July 26, 2019 Friday]

37:52.680 --> 37:55.530
[July 26, 2019 Friday]

37:58.590 --> 38:05.030
[July 26, 2019 Friday]

38:13.430 --> 38:14.980
[Unknown Caller]

38:17.110 --> 38:18.190
Dr. Luo, morning.

38:18.630 --> 38:19.160
Morning.

38:20.230 --> 38:21.090
Morning shift?

38:21.440 --> 38:21.960
Yes.

38:31.960 --> 38:32.360
Hello?

38:32.720 --> 38:33.320
Dr. Luo,

38:33.920 --> 38:34.980
this is Officer Li.

38:36.190 --> 38:36.920
Officer Li,

38:37.480 --> 38:38.280
what is it now?

38:39.480 --> 38:41.800
Could you come to the police station now?

38:43.880 --> 38:44.480
Right now?

38:45.710 --> 38:46.360
Sorry.

38:46.800 --> 38:48.030
This is not a proper time.

38:48.030 --> 38:48.890
I'm on duty now.

38:50.070 --> 38:51.930
Didn't Yan Ling already tell you?

38:52.280 --> 38:54.540
We've cooperated in every way we should.

38:55.150 --> 38:57.080
Please stop disturbing our lives.

38:57.480 --> 38:58.150
Here's the thing.

38:58.150 --> 38:59.400
Regarding Qiao Zishan's case,

38:59.400 --> 39:01.200
we need to take some statements.

39:01.480 --> 39:02.960
Every citizen is obligated to cooperate

39:02.960 --> 39:04.620
with police investigations.

39:05.360 --> 39:06.690
Please be cooperative,

39:06.760 --> 39:07.440
will you?

39:12.030 --> 39:12.550
Fine.

39:17.250 --> 39:19.180
[Loyal to the Party, Serve the People]

39:18.000 --> 39:18.400
Sit.

39:26.400 --> 39:27.310
Relax.

39:27.440 --> 39:28.440
We just need a statement from you.

39:28.440 --> 39:29.840
It's routine procedure.

39:36.760 --> 39:38.960
Qiao Zishan's condition has improved.

39:40.550 --> 39:41.110
Really?

39:42.000 --> 39:43.060
That's great news.

39:44.670 --> 39:47.110
But she insists
that she knocked down her mother

39:47.110 --> 39:48.890
by accident during the fire.

39:49.000 --> 39:50.230
So, over all these years,

39:50.230 --> 39:51.190
she's been beating herself up,

39:51.190 --> 39:53.450
thinking that she killed her own mother.

39:56.360 --> 39:58.020
Her life is miserable enough.

39:58.800 --> 40:00.590
Frankly speaking, I really don't know

40:00.590 --> 40:02.320
why you have to add to her pain.

40:03.230 --> 40:05.360
The guilt and self-blame
weighing on her heart

40:05.360 --> 40:07.190
have exceeded what she can take.

40:08.000 --> 40:09.460
This is why she broke down,

40:10.030 --> 40:12.560
and her mental state didn't improve
in years.

40:15.800 --> 40:16.760
We retrieved the forensic report

40:16.760 --> 40:19.360
written by the Harbor Island police
back then.

40:19.590 --> 40:20.480
This report shows

40:20.480 --> 40:22.670
that Qiao Zishan's mother, Qiao Lihua,

40:22.670 --> 40:25.270
did have multiple injuries
caused by tumbles.

40:25.880 --> 40:27.280
But recently, we sent the report

40:27.280 --> 40:28.920
to a rather experienced forensic expert

40:28.920 --> 40:29.840
in the mainland.

40:29.840 --> 40:30.840
He pointed out...

40:33.280 --> 40:35.530
that there was a radiating fracture

40:36.000 --> 40:38.030
on the left temporal side
of the deceased's skull,

40:38.030 --> 40:40.430
likely resulting from blunt force trauma.

40:49.190 --> 40:49.880
Sorry,

40:49.880 --> 40:50.540
Officer Li.

40:51.590 --> 40:52.920
I am a psychiatrist

40:53.840 --> 40:56.190
who has no expertise in forensic science.

40:58.630 --> 40:59.430
I understand.

41:00.880 --> 41:02.540
Today, I asked you to come over

41:02.630 --> 41:04.440
because I'd like you to tell me

41:05.000 --> 41:06.440
if there was anyone else

41:06.880 --> 41:08.440
than you, Qiao Zishan, and her mother

41:07.020 --> 41:10.960
[Suspected to be caused by a blunt object
with a curved impact face]

41:09.230 --> 41:10.760
at the fire scene years ago.

41:11.200 --> 41:12.840
Could someone have caused this injury

41:12.840 --> 41:14.460
by hitting Qiao Lihua in the head

41:14.460 --> 41:15.840
with a heavy object?

41:24.070 --> 41:25.470
I can't recall anything.

41:26.030 --> 41:28.530
All I can remember
is that the whole place was a total mess

41:28.530 --> 41:30.330
when the fire fighters arrived.

41:35.640 --> 41:40.010
[Suspected to be caused by a blunt object
with a curved impact face]

41:38.800 --> 41:40.410
It says "suspected."

41:40.550 --> 41:42.670
Could it have been caused

41:42.670 --> 41:43.840
by the burned furniture

41:43.840 --> 41:45.440
or some sort of heavy object?

41:46.230 --> 41:48.430
That could be a possibility, of course.

41:48.880 --> 41:50.630
But according to the forensic expert,

41:50.630 --> 41:53.590
the contact surface of the wound
suggests the assault weapon

41:53.590 --> 41:55.650
should be a sphere-shaped object.

41:56.590 --> 41:58.920
Furniture doesn't fit that description.

42:00.850 --> 42:03.180
Back then, in Dr. Tao's office,

42:04.070 --> 42:04.760
was there

42:05.590 --> 42:07.720
any heavy object resembling a sphere?

42:10.960 --> 42:11.960
I don't remember.

42:16.480 --> 42:17.680
Well, that's a shame.

42:19.190 --> 42:21.120
See, if we really find this object,

42:21.800 --> 42:23.280
with current technology,

42:23.300 --> 42:26.050
as long as there is a tiny bit
of biological residue on it,

42:26.050 --> 42:27.850
we'll be able to find DNA traces.

42:28.480 --> 42:30.810
Then the truth will be revealed, won't it?

42:31.070 --> 42:31.880
It can also save you

42:31.880 --> 42:33.280
the trouble of coming over
every now and then

42:33.280 --> 42:34.960
to assist us with the investigation.

42:34.960 --> 42:35.360
Right?

42:38.880 --> 42:40.680
I'm terribly sorry, Officer Li,

42:41.670 --> 42:43.270
for not being helpful at all.

42:44.260 --> 42:48.790
[The Dark Romance]
